## Pipeline Commercial (Kanban)

```
NEW → SCREENING → MEETING → PROPOSAL → CUSTOMER
```

Les montants sont en **micros** : `amountMicros: 50000000000` = **50 000 €** (diviser par 1 000 000)

---

## Exemples API

### Créer une company
```graphql
mutation {
  createCompany(data: {
    name: "Cabinet Dupont"
    domainName: { primaryLinkUrl: "https://dupont-avocat.fr" }
    employees: 5
  }) {
    id name
  }
}
```

### Créer un contact
```graphql
mutation {
  createPerson(data: {
    name: { firstName: "Jean", lastName: "Dupont" }
    emails: { primaryEmail: "jean@dupont-avocat.fr" }
    phones: { primaryPhoneNumber: "+33612345678" }
    jobTitle: "Avocat associé"
    companyId: "<company-uuid>"
  }) {
    id
  }
}
```

### Créer une opportunité
```graphql
mutation {
  createOpportunity(data: {
    name: "Collaborateur IA - Dupont"
    stage: NEW
    amount: { amountMicros: 500000000, currencyCode: "EUR" }
    closeDate: "2026-05-01T00:00:00Z"
    companyId: "<company-uuid>"
    pointOfContactId: "<person-uuid>"
    ownerId: "4d1953bf-b35b-4c63-84ff-ba15303e9e9a"
  }) {
    id
  }
}
```

### Requête curl
```bash
API_KEY=$(python3 tools/get_credential.py twenty-crm api_key)
curl -s -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:3002/graphql" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"query":"{ companies(first: 10) { edges { node { id name } } } }"}'
```

